full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/5/2023 AMERICAN EMBASSY DIPLOMATIC ENCLAVE, RAMNA 5 ISLAMABAD LIST OF APPROVED PHYSICIANS FOR MEDICAL EXAMINATIONS FOR VISAS The following physicians is Karachi, Lahore and Islamabad have been approved by the American Embassy for the purposes of medical examinations for United States Visas. Medical examinations are required as part of an application for an immigrant visa to the United States, must be completed and brought at the time of interview. They are to be done from one of the following doctors: 1. DR. AHMED RAZA JAN DR.
